WEBVTT

00:02:58.863 --> 00:03:01.204
ukikichomoa kwa dakika chache --

00:03:01.228 --> 00:03:03.923
(Vicheko)

00:03:03.947 --> 00:03:07.229
(Makofi)

00:03:07.253 --> 00:03:08.976
hata na wewe.

00:03:10.975 --> 00:03:14.213
Tatu: karibia, hakuna chochote nje ya wewe

00:03:14.237 --> 00:03:17.149
kitakachokusaidia kwa njia yoyote ya kudumu,

00:03:17.173 --> 00:03:19.137
isipokuwa kama unasubiria kiungo.

00:03:19.958 --> 00:03:24.896
Huwezi kununua, kutekeleza au kuchumbia utulivu na amani.

00:03:24.920 --> 00:03:28.694
Huu ni kweli ya kutisha,
na ninauchukia.

00:03:29.549 --> 00:03:31.773
Lakini ni kazi ya ndani,